snippet.title: Battle RC | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's finally out! With many bots to play with, battle against friends or AI in this new robot combat game. Battle RC is out on Steam, check it out!

Get it now on Steam:
https://blastergames.org/

Check out the subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Battle_RC/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/kBGtEP4JSU
